params.name: data.directories_found_from_source
params.description: For transfers involving PosixFilesystem only. Number of directories found while listing. For example, if the root directory of the transfer is base/ and there are two other directories, a/ and b/ under this directory, the count after listing base/, base/a/ and base/b/ is 3.

params.description: For transfers involving PosixFilesystem only. Number of listing failures for each directory found at the source. Potential failures when listing a directory include permission failure or block failure. If listing a directory fails, no files in the directory are transferred.
